This Week in the SEC for Oct. 24, 2015 Thursday, October 22, 2015 
Here's a preview of SEC football games scheduled for Saturday, Oct. 24, 2015. 
(Times are Central Daylight.) 
Use the links below to access the full feature. Document 
Tennessee at Alabama, 2:30 p.m. Sat. on CBS

Auburn at Arkansas, 11 a.m. Sat. on SEC 
Texas A&M at Mississippi, 6 p.m. Sat. on ESPN 
Kentucky at Mississippi State, 6:30 p.m. Sat. on SEC 
Rounding It Out

Western Kentucky at LSU, 6 p.m. Sat. on ESPNU
